cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.DC 

The paper is about optimizing deep learning using backpropagation algorithm, which is a core topic in machine learning. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also discusses the optimization of neural networks, which falls under cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Additionally, the paper focuses on training deep convolutional neural networks, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also discusses stochastic methods, which are commonly used in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and distributed computing (cs.DC).
